Don't get so close!

133
00:14:05,717 --> 00:14:09,153
<i>How did those guys manage to get out?</i>

134
00:14:10,221 --> 00:14:11,449
<i>Not only that...</i>

135
00:14:12,591 --> 00:14:14,650
<i>What are these black flames?</i>

136
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:19,719
