147
00:16:08,206 --> 00:16:09,764
Well... Eh...

148
00:16:09,841 --> 00:16:12,469
I'm sorry to have kicked you so directly.

149
00:16:12,977 --> 00:16:15,878
I was in a rush and I forgot my mirror...

150
00:16:18,249 --> 00:16:21,218
I used this headband instead,
but it was hard to see.

151
00:16:21,286 --> 00:16:23,379
And I assumed this rough hewn face
was the enemy...

152
00:16:23,455 --> 00:16:26,322
