the burning juvenescence take over me...

153
00:16:26,725 --> 00:16:27,589
I'm sorry!

154
00:16:27,659 --> 00:16:31,322
Is that... supposed to be an apology?

155
00:16:31,896 --> 00:16:34,160
I'm a simple minded guy
just like how my face looks.

156
00:16:34,632 --> 00:16:36,532
It doesn't really matter.

157
00:16:37,135 --> 00:16:40,195
More importantly, we have to get Sasuke
to the Medical Team!

158
00:16:40,271 --> 00:16:41,067
Yes!

159
00:16:41,272 --> 00:16:44,207
He's broken his arm and ribs.

160
00:16:44,976 --> 00:16:47,308
Not only that, he's lost consciousness

161
00:16:47,378 --> 00:16:49,710
