he received from the Visual Jutsu!

162
00:16:51,683 --> 00:16:53,617
<i>This boy also experienced that Jutsu...</i>

163
00:16:54,552 --> 00:16:58,283
Hey Pervy Sage!
Is Sasuke going to be all right?

164
00:16:59,958 --> 00:17:03,860
