a significant amount of mental damage.

165
00:17:07,766 --> 00:17:10,234
<i>I'm going to kill you!</i>

166
00:17:18,109 --> 00:17:19,337
<i>Die!</i>

167
00:17:45,069 --> 00:17:45,797
<i>You jerk!</i>

168
00:17:45,870 --> 00:17:46,564
<i>You're in the way!</i>

169
00:18:05,957 --> 00:18:10,018
<i>Darn... Why?!</i>

170
00:18:10,528 --> 00:18:14,157
<i>What did that guy do to Sasuke?!</i>

171
00:18:14,232 --> 00:18:15,790
Hey, Pervy Sage!

172
00:18:17,435 --> 00:18:18,925
We've gotta change our plan!

173
00:18:19,637 --> 00:18:21,264
I got scared earlier,

174
00:18:21,339 --> 00:18:26,402
but this time I'm going to chase
those black capes and get them!

175
00:18:26,845 --> 00:18:29,040
It's me that they want, right?!

176
00:18:30,615 --> 00:18:33,243
Then, I'll be the one to
make my way over!

177
00:18:34,085 --> 00:18:38,749
Humph, you're only going to be killed
if you go now.

178
00:18:40,124 --> 00:18:41,682
They're at a totally different level
from you.

179
00:18:42,727 --> 00:18:47,858
I just managed to get you
away from them...

180
00:18:48,733 --> 00:18:52,430
Then, are we just going
to keep running away?!

181
00:18:52,971 --> 00:18:56,338
Are we supposed to keep living in fear?!

182
00:18:57,108 --> 00:18:58,302
Shut your mouth for a second!

183
00:19:04,148 --> 00:19:05,615
You are weak.

184
00:19:10,488 --> 00:19:11,750
I'm sorry, Guy.

185
00:19:12,056 --> 00:19:14,581
I thought that I had spared
the boy's feeling, but...

186
00:19:15,226 --> 00:19:18,286
I should have saved him much sooner.

187
00:19:20,665 --> 00:19:24,533
