he will regain consciousness.

189
00:19:27,805 --> 00:19:29,033
Kakashi Sensei?!

190
00:19:45,256 --> 00:19:47,554
When my students are hurt...

191
00:19:48,793 --> 00:19:51,455
I always wish,
from the bottom of my heart...

192
00:19:52,430 --> 00:19:57,595
If that person,
who is a medical specialist, were here...

193
00:20:01,339 --> 00:20:05,298
That's why we're going to
go find her now.

194
00:20:05,710 --> 00:20:06,574
What?

195
00:20:07,045 --> 00:20:08,342
You mean, her?

196
00:20:22,026 --> 00:20:23,118
Could it be...?

197
00:20:34,839 --> 00:20:37,205
W-Wait...!

198
00:20:37,575 --> 00:20:40,203
C-Could this money be...?!

199
00:20:40,778 --> 00:20:42,939
Yup, that's right...

200
00:20:43,781 --> 00:20:46,147
The one who uses the slug
and drives illness away,

201
00:20:46,217 --> 00:20:48,708
and who is also
one of the Sannin like me...

202
00:20:49,487 --> 00:20:54,481
All right! We're going to turn around
our luck with this!

203
00:20:55,326 --> 00:20:59,695
Princess Tsunade with
the letter Gamble on her back!

204
00:21:09,407 --> 00:21:13,343
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

205
00:21:14,346 --> 00:21:18,305
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

206
00:21:19,618 --> 00:21:27,582
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

207
00:21:28,560 --> 00:21:30,653
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

208
00:21:33,431 --> 00:21:36,457
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

209
00:21:36,901 --> 00:21:41,838
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

210
00:21:41,973 --> 00:21:47,434
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

211
00:21:47,712 --> 00:21:52,615
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

212
00:21:52,684 --> 00:21:57,587
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

213
00:21:57,656 --> 00:22:06,826
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

214
00:22:07,265 --> 00:22:12,168
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

215
00:22:12,237 --> 00:22:18,073
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

216
00:22:19,711 --> 00:22:29,848
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

217
00:22:36,161 --> 00:22:37,753
It's festival, festival, festival!

218
00:22:37,896 --> 00:22:39,557
I'm going to spend like
there's no tomorrow!

219
00:22:39,631 --> 00:22:42,828
Wait a minute, Naruto!
I will keep your wallet for you.

220
00:22:42,901 --> 00:22:43,526
Huh?!

221
00:22:43,601 --> 00:22:46,001
It's been said since ages past
that three forbidden factors:

222
00:22:46,071 --> 00:22:49,734
Money, alcohol, and women,
are believed to cause Ninja failures.

223
00:22:49,808 --> 00:22:52,402
I am not like you, Pervy Sage!

224
00:22:52,477 --> 00:22:55,446
All right! I am going to
enjoy the festival!

225
00:22:56,114 --> 00:22:59,948
Next time: "A New Training Begins:
I Will Be Strong!"

226
00:23:00,218 --> 00:23:02,482
Wait. What are we gonna
do about my training?
